'''真空飛船'''（Vacuum Airship）是一種以[[真空|真空]]容器取代[[氫氣|氫氣]]容器或[[氦氣|氦氣]]容器來提供[[升力|升力]]的假想中的[[飞艇_(轻航空器)|飛船]]。此構想最早由義大利的Francesco Lana de Terzi在1670年提出<ref>{{Cite web | title = Francesco Lana-Terzi, S.J. (1631-1687); The Father of Aeronautics | url = http://www.faculty.fairfield.edu/jmac/sj/scientists/lana.htm | accessdate = 13 November 2009 | archive-date = 2021-04-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210424104423/http://www.faculty.fairfield.edu/jmac/sj/scientists/lana.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>，真空球是浮力升力終極的實現方法。

